This paper is about adversarial attacks for image classification, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). The paper also discusses optimization methods for solving the constrained minimization problem, which could fall under cryptography and security (cs.CR). Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.LG and cs.CV, followed by cs.AI, cs.NE, and cs.CR.
